&lt;p&gt;Digible, Inc. is looking for an &lt;strong&gt;Account Manager&lt;/strong&gt; to join our team!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our Client Services department is responsible for cultivating extraordinary relationships with Digible’s agency and tech clients, making strategic recommendations that demonstrate a deep understanding of client goals, and ensuring digital campaigns and products are meeting or exceeding expectations.&lt;/p&gt;
